{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_01","textHome":"我叫江利爱实！大家，请多指教？@啊！糟、糟糕！他……是在……看我吗！？@怎、怎么办……怎么办……那个……嗯……@爱、爱好是幻想……不！是做点心之类的……@我、我在找……接受我亲手做的点心的人……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_18","textHome":"现在的我，不管是什么样的对手出现，@我都能用势不可挡的力量取得胜利！@漫画中也见过的吧？横插一手的角色？@那种真是最讨厌了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_19","textHome":"不要不要！我讨厌极限！@因为恋爱故事是永远的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_20","textHome":"啊——舒服了！恋爱的烦恼也消……没有消失@！没有消——失！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":400}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_21","textHome":"好难受！悲伤涌上了心头！@恋爱，为什么这么悲伤呢？@不过，这就是恋爱的妙趣么？@那么我就用全力去体会吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_22","textHome":"不管怎么烦恼，我都放不下这份感情！@这之后我肯定还会因为害怕被讨厌，@一直苦恼个不停……不过！我已经决定了，@我要追随这份感情勇往直前！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_23","textHome":"够了！好吧！将错就错？……不对，@不能叫将错就错……正因为喜欢才会烦恼嘛！@烦恼才是恋爱的证明对吧？那样就没问题啦！@我今后也会全力去恋爱的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_24","textHome":"啊！我在等你呢！我已经等不及了！@快点快点！恋爱商谈！你能给我建议吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_25","textHome":"嗯——虽然很困，但还是要振作起来……！@一大早就清爽地用“早上好”打招呼的女生，@不就像广告里拍的一样美好嘛？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_26","textHome":"肚子饿了……好想吃上一大碗牛肉盖浇饭……@不过，女孩子吃那么粗野的东西大概会很@引人注目吧……！？我还是吃三明治吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_27","textHome":"呐呐——我们去咖啡店吧！@去咖啡店聊点恋爱话题吧！@没关系没关系！这方面的话题我多的是！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_03","textHome":"我最喜欢女子会了！热烈的恋爱话题最棒了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_28","textHome":"我讨厌夜晚。一到夜晚我就会胡思乱想……@像是“其实我根本不喜欢他”，@或者“要是被甩了怎么办”什么的……@一想到这些就停不下来。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_29","textHome":"和朋友聊天的时候我就显得很自然，放的开。@要是和他也能这样聊天就好了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_30","textHome":"嗯！因为我的本职是恋爱！@所以魔法少女的工作就赶快完成吧！@喂，走吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_31","textHome":"是谁堵在我面前，妨碍我恋爱的人不可饶恕！@我也是有认真的时候的哦？看我恋爱的力量！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_32","textHome":"太好了！这就是魔法少女同伴的聚集时间吗？@等战斗结束了，我要向她们咨询各种事情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_33","textHome":"你知道恋爱化妆品吗？@只要用了就能实现恋爱的东西！@不过，不都说男孩子更喜欢天然美吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_34","textHome":"“爱实……我其实也一直喜欢着你……”@他要是一边这么说着，一边做些什么的话！@呀！真是的，该怎么办啊——！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_35","textHome":"幻想和自己喜欢的人发生各种展开之类的……@不可以吗？大家不都是这么做的吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_36","textHome":"突然改变形象，没准就能牢牢抓住他的心！@虽然也这么想过，但要是失败了的话……@那就太可怕了，所以还是维持现状吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_37","textHome":"我喜欢的人，超级超级帅的哦？@真的！就像从少女漫画里出来的一样！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_04","textHome":"怎么办才好啊！？到底该怎么办啊！"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_38","textHome":"我最喜欢女子会了！热烈的恋爱话题最棒了！@从认识了各种各样的女孩子的意义上来说，@能成为魔法少女真是太好了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_39","textHome":"朋友说我平常的情绪太过于高涨，@稍微扭捏一些的话就刚好了……@嗯……是这样的吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_40","textHome":"我不太擅长和男孩子说话……@并不是讨厌男孩子哦？因为，会很紧张吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_41","textHome":"我成为魔法少女时许的愿望是，@想知道他对我的感情！你问结果？@结果是……唔呼！唔呼呼呼呼呼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_42","textHome":"等等！不要打扰我啊！？"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_43","textHome":"好的好的！下次再见！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_44","textHome":"不能让喜欢的人等着对吧！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_45","textHome":"恋爱中的少女的力量，体会到了吗？"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_46","textHome":"“青春短暂的少女哟恋爱吧！”是吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_63","textHome":"恋爱的力量充满了全身!!"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_05","textHome":"啊，舒服了！@感觉恋爱的烦恼也消……没有消失！@没有消——失！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":400}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_64","textHome":"这份感情已经无法被任何人阻止了——！！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_65","textHome":"阻碍我恋爱的人我要统统铲除——！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302300,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_66","textHome":"在成为情侣之前我是不会死的！！"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_02","textHome":"我？我是江利爱实哟！啊！虽然有些突然，@你能给我的恋爱提一些建议吗？@哎——那可真是太辛苦了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_13","textHome":"嗯？我变强了吗？变强了之后会更有魅力吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_14","textHome":"太好了！我的兴致也达到了最高点！@向着两情相悦奔跑吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_15","textHome":"总之只要前进就行了！呼……！@拿出干劲来呀，爱实！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_16","textHome":"嗯嗯，感觉不错……！@就这样子，射中他的心吧……！砰，砰……！@嘿嘿！讨厌啦，开个玩笑嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3023_00_17","textHome":"哈！我想到了！超级无敌，一定能让对方@心动的约会计划！趁着没忘，我要赶紧@把它记在笔记上才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302300,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}